  </li>
</ul>

<h2 id="more-details">More Details</h2>

<p>On March 19, 2020, NHL Seattle CEO Tod Leiweke emailed all fans and premium season ticket holders in two separate emails.</p>

<p>In his email to fans, Lieweke announced a few key changes to NHL Seattle‚Äôs planned events.</p>

